01:44:36.125 --> 01:44:38.916
Atas nama Ibu Zalina Anindita, ya?
Tujuan ke Bali.

1374
01:44:39.000 --> 01:44:40.666
- Terima kasih.
- Terima kasih.

1375
01:44:40.750 --> 01:44:41.958
Yuk, Sayang.

1376
01:44:42.500 --> 01:44:43.708
Silakan.

1377
01:44:43.791 --> 01:44:45.291
Dibantu tiketnya?

1378
01:44:49.250 --> 01:44:52.458
[Arlo] Ponsel Zalina tidak aktif terus.
Bagaimana ini, Ma?

1379
01:45:00.541 --> 01:45:03.625
[berbisik samar]

1380
01:45:08.583 --> 01:45:12.208
[staf bandara] Selamat siang.
Tujuan Bali, ya? Dibantu tiketnya?

1381
01:45:13.833 --> 01:45:16.666
- Silakan pas naiknya. Terima kasih.
- Oke. Terima kasih, Mas.

1382
01:45:18.916 --> 01:45:21.458
Ma. Doakan Arlo, ya, Ma.

1383
01:45:23.041 --> 01:45:26.083
Mama doakan yang terbaik
untuk kalian berdua.

1384
01:45:28.125 --> 01:45:29.708
Hati-hati, Sayang.

1385
01:45:29.791 --> 01:45:34.250
[musik lembut mengalun]

1386
01:45:37.750 --> 01:45:38.958
[Zalina] Terima kasih.

1387
01:45:42.916 --> 01:45:44.208
Zalina!

1388
01:45:46.791 --> 01:45:48.208
Om Arlo!

1389
01:45:53.541 --> 01:45:55.291
[Arlo] Halo, Arka.

1390
01:45:56.166 --> 01:45:59.958
- Arka rindu Om Arlo.
- [Arlo] Om Arlo juga.

1391
01:46:00.041 --> 01:46:03.083
[musik romantis mengalun]

1392
01:46:09.791 --> 01:46:10.791
Hai.

1393
01:46:13.916 --> 01:46:17.416
Kamu… Kamu di sini?

1394
01:46:21.250 --> 01:46:23.500
Mama sudah merestui hubungan kita, Za.

1395
01:46:27.916 --> 01:46:29.375
Zalina Anindita…

1396
01:46:30.875 --> 01:46:33.750
Karena ketentuan
yang telah Allah perintahkan…

1397
01:46:36.250 --> 01:46:38.000
aku ingin menjadi imam

1398
01:46:39.708 --> 01:46:41.666
untuk membimbing keluarga kita nanti.

1399
01:46:41.750 --> 01:46:45.541
[musik romantis berlanjut]

1400
01:46:45.625 --> 01:46:46.500
Aku…

1401
01:46:47.208 --> 01:46:48.250
Kamu…

1402
01:46:49.208 --> 01:46:50.375
Arka…

1403
01:46:53.458 --> 01:46:55.375
Untuk menuju jalan yang lurus

1404
01:46:56.666 --> 01:46:59.208
dan berjuang bersama menuju surga-Nya.

1405
01:47:03.000 --> 01:47:04.208
[terisak]

1406
01:47:14.041 --> 01:47:15.750
Maukah kamu jadi istri aku?

1407
01:47:21.833 --> 01:47:25.333
[terisak]

1408
01:47:28.208 --> 01:47:29.875
Mas Arlo.

1409
01:47:31.791 --> 01:47:34.500
Setelah apa yang sudah aku lalui…

1410
01:47:36.583 --> 01:47:39.708
aku… butuh waktu, Mas.

1411
01:47:39.791 --> 01:47:41.958
[menghela napas]

1412
01:47:43.666 --> 01:47:45.000
[bahasa Inggris] Tidak.

1413
01:47:45.083 --> 01:47:46.916
[bahasa Indonesia] Tunggu apa lagi, Za?

1414
01:47:47.750 --> 01:47:50.000
Aku sudah memperjuangkan restu dari Mama.

1415
01:47:52.166 --> 01:47:56.375
Aku janji, aku akan
membahagiakan kamu dan Arka.

1416
01:47:57.666 --> 01:47:58.750
[bahasa Inggris] Kumohon.

1417
01:48:01.291 --> 01:48:02.375
Kumohon.

1418
01:48:02.958 --> 01:48:04.916
Tolong, Mama! Tolong!

1419
01:48:06.458 --> 01:48:09.125
Tolong…

1420
01:48:13.958 --> 01:48:14.875
[terisak]

1421
01:48:26.333 --> 01:48:28.625
[bahasa Indonesia] Bismillah.

1422
01:48:30.791 --> 01:48:32.041
Mas Arlo.

1423
01:48:35.666 --> 01:48:38.375
Aku bersedia dinikahi kamu.

1424
01:48:40.166 --> 01:48:42.041
Alhamdulillah!

1425
01:48:42.125 --> 01:48:46.833
[musik bahagia mengalun]

1426
01:49:00.375 --> 01:49:03.208
Arka, mulai hari ini,

1427
01:49:03.291 --> 01:49:05.583
Arka sudah boleh
panggil Om Arlo "Papa", ya.

1428
01:49:05.666 --> 01:49:07.875
[terkesiap] Hore!

1429
01:49:07.958 --> 01:49:11.500
Asyik, punya papa!

1430
01:49:11.583 --> 01:49:12.583
Hore!

1431
01:49:13.666 --> 01:49:15.291
[tertawa pelan]

1432
01:49:15.375 --> 01:49:19.250
- [bahasa Inggris] Bahagia bersama.
- Bahagia bersama.

